{"title":"乘车","authors":["于之"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒假过去了，小朋友们要上学了。我们发表这组儿童诗，作为一点小小的礼物。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小杨姊姊毕业了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当了公共汽车售票员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她每天下班回家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要大弟找小朋友来玩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报纸裁成车票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桌椅搭成车厢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大弟当了司机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"售票员就是小杨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘客来了几十个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搀着布娃娃，抱着花猫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上了车纷纷买票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你到城站，他去大桥……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呜呜，汽车在飞跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车厢里又挤又闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小花猫忽然逃走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小妈妈急得哭了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"售票员不慌不忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手比蝴蝶灵巧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安排小妈妈坐下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找回了淘气的花猫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钟还不到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖了五十张车票！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还给小熊量了高度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要它买张半票。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮这位扶一把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮那位提包包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把乘客都当亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘客都说姊姊好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姊姊谢谢小朋友："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天帮她做练习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来她一分钟卖二十张车票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在能卖五十七。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姊姊又谢谢大弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说他安全行车已十万公里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车子开得又快又稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将来准是个真正的司机！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}